These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, scientist, social-worker
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, bike
1. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
2. the social-worker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
3. the person driving the bike is between the scientist and the social-worker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Job         | scientist | firefighter   | social-worker |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bike | bus        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, coffee
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, dog
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
3. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | coffee | lemonade   | sprite   |
| Pet        | horse | dog | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
There 3 different types of food: banana, kale, eggplant
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, ship, quad-bike
1. the person eating banana is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
2. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the person eating banana and the person driving the trike##7
3. the person eating eggplant is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
4. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Food        | kale | eggplant | banana |
| Transport   | trike       | quad-bike     | ship         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, librarian, paramedic
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, epic, crime
1. the paramedic is not to the right of the librarian##8
2. the paramedic is on the right of the manager##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching epic movies and the manager##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | manager | paramedic | librarian |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | superhero | epic    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, zombie, horror
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
3. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
4. the person watching zombie movies is not to the right of the person watching romance movies##8
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | horror | romance |
| Pet           | lizard    | guinea-pig      | chinchilla  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
