.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, milk, lemonade
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, entrepreneur, journalist
1. the entrepreneur is between the journalist and the person drinking lemonade##2
2. the person drinking milk is not to the left of the journalist##8
3. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the journalist##8
4. the journalist is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | water | milk | lemonade |
| Job        | journalist      | entrepreneur    | videographer |

