2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching epic movies is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Food          | artichoke | spinach  | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel     | epic | satire   |

