The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball, snowboarding
1. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
3. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage   | coffee | water        | cola    |
| Sport      | volleyball  | snowboarding | surfing |

