2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of funk is between the fan of punk and the fan of blues##2
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the fan of punk is not to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | funk      | punk |
| Sport         | baseball | biathlon | cricket     |

