3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
4. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
5. the person eating potato is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | pumpkin | potato | mango    |
