3. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the person watching musical movies and the person watching horror movies##7
4. the person watching horror movies is not to the left of the german##8
5. the german is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | crime    | horror  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | thai | german |

