There are 3 different nationalities: polish, japanese, nigerian
1. the japanese is somewhere between the nigerian and the person who's hobby is hiking##7
2. the polish is not to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
3. the polish is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby         | singing | gardening | hiking |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | japanese    | polish    |

 